title: Quick Stitch Crochet: Time Saving Designs for Home and Family
description: This new collection of patterns can be completed in a weekend or less. This book offers appealing selections in home decor, accessories and fashions in a wide variety of stitches, techniques, yarns and color palettes. Whether making these beautiful designs as gifts or sprucing up your own decor or wardrobe, you're sure to find time to crochet as many as you like with these time-saving designs.
